Package com.example.multimedia

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameActivity
    GameActivity holds the GameSurfaceView and Gameloop
    GameLoop
    GameLoop implements Thread methods, calls update and render methods in GameSurfaceView and calculates average FPS/UPS
    GameOverActivity
    GameOverActivity holds the Game Over Screen
    GameSurfaceView
    GameSurfaceView holds all objects of the game, implements update and render methods
    GameWinActivity
    GameOverActivity holds the Game Win Screen and displays points earned
    HighscoreActivity
    HighscoreActivity contains the highscores which are displayed using a RecyclerView
    HighscoreAdapter
    HighscoreAdapter is a RecyclerView Adapter that holds the individual Highscore elements (implemented in HighscoreViewHolder)
    HighscoreViewHolder
    HighscoreViewHolder holds an individual element of the RecyclerView (implemented in layout file highscore_item.xml)
    IntroScreen  
    IntroVideoActivity
    IntroVideoActivity holds the Intro Video Player
    LevelMap
    LevelMap holds one game level and handles drawing and interaction with game objects (items and points)
    LevelSelectActivity
    LevelSelectActivity holds the Level selection screen.
    MainActivity
    MainActivity is the entryway to our application.
    MusicPlayer
    Handles access to the background music, so it can be accessed over different activities.
    TutorialScreen
